 trailing edge with a cusp-like shape\nand also exhibits the negative wake phenomena. However, a viscoelastic bubble\nrising in a Newtonian fluid develops an indentation around the rear stagnation\npoint with a dimpled shape.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2019 09:00:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-19"}
