of the fundamental solution for such operators\ndepends on the dimension. Indeed, we show that we have even sign change for a\nsuitable operator of order $2m$ in dimension $n=2m+2$. On the other hand we\nshow that in the dimensions $n=2m$ and $n=2m+1$ the fundamental solution of any\nsuch elliptic operator is always positive around its singularity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2019 10:44:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Apr 2020 08:33:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-08"}
