 effect at room temperature in\nnano-Hall bars prepared at the same time as the spin Hall devices. Large\nanomalous Hall conductivity along with adequate spin Hall conductivity makes\nMn$_3$Sn a promising material for ultrafast and ultrahigh-density spintronics\ndevices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2019 11:08:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-22"}
