e applied for prediction of\nother rock properties (residual brine and oil saturations, relative\npermeability, capillary pressure, and others), which laboratory measurements\nare time-consuming and expensive.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2019 11:37:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-19"}
