ted by the complete\ntwo - point Green function with the interactions included. Basing on the\nobtained expressions we discuss the topological phase transitions accompanied\nby the change of Hall conductivity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2019 12:41:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Mar 2019 12:45:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 27 May 2019 09:52:23 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 22 Apr 2021 17:36:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-23"}
